Free Service
Sir 

this complaint is with regard to free service. I have bought  Breeza ZDI + and today my second free service is due. I have come to competent automobiles at Mandi. They are charging for wheel alingment and wheel balancing. I am surprised when I saked them to justify me about the labour charges which they are charging from cousyomer under free service. The executive as well as their officer have abrupltely replied to me me that agr karwani hai to karwao koi jabrdasti nahin hai. Such kind of reply from the business executives are not expected at all. Moreover the staff is not co operative with the customers no one is able to assist the customers in justified manner. Competent Mandi is providing very bad  infact worse service to the customers. 


Sushil Jaswal
