Company Description                    




                        Competent Automobiles Company Limited, incorporated in 1985, engages in trading and servicing Maruti Suzuki vehicles in India. The company's  Showroom segment involves in the purchase and sale of new vehicles of Maruti Suzuki India Limited while its Services and Spares segment engages in servicing, as well as the sale of spare parts of Maruti Suzuki India Limited. The company has its registered office located in Delhi.
                    


